sentences: Anders Nyström (born 22 April 1975), also known as Blakkheim (or formerly Blackheim), is a Swedish musician.
Nyström founded the Swedish metal band Katatonia with singer Jonas Renkse in 1991.
He used to be a member of the metal band Bewitched from 1995 to 1997 and is still with Jonas Renkse on the death metal project Bloodbath.
Cancer – guitar on the track "Ballcutter" from the album Shadow Gripped (2019)
